[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     99[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    100[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    101[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # These thresholds are calibrated for the synthetic data in this example.
