[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    122[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    123[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### NOTE 2: `referral_breadth` is an integer count treated as a continuous metric in O/E adjustment
